    "id": "nce1-099-100-ow",
    "title": "Lesson 99: Ow!",
    "audioFilename": "099&100－Ow.mp3",
    "duration": 72.673,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.34,
      "end": 1.96,
      "text": "Lesson 99.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第99课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 4.78,
      "end": 8.98,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 10.7,
      "end": 13.38,
      "text": "Must Andy go to see the doctor?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "安迪必须去看医生吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 17.01,
      "end": 19.11,
      "text": "What's the matter, Andy?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "怎么了，安迪？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 19.83,
      "end": 22.67,
      "text": "I slipped and fell downstairs.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我滑了一跤，从楼梯上摔了下来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 23.73,
      "end": 25.51,
      "text": "Have you hurt yourself?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你伤着自己了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 26.17,
      "end": 27.55,
      "text": "Yes, I have.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是的，伤着了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 27.55,
      "end": 31.19,
      "text": "I think that I've hurt my back.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我想我的背受伤了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 32.75,
      "end": 34.43,
      "text": "Try and stand up.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "试着站起来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 35.31,
      "end": 36.89,
      "text": "Can you stand up?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你能站起来吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 37.49,
      "end": 40.05,
      "text": "Here, let me help you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "来，让我帮你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 41.39,
      "end": 42.77,
      "text": "I'm sorry, Lucy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "对不起，露西。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 43.83,
      "end": 46.63,
      "text": "I'm afraid that I can't get up.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "恐怕我站不起来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 47.91,
      "end": 52.15,
      "text": "I think that the doctor had better see you.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我想最好让医生给你看看。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 52.99,
      "end": 54.65,
      "text": "I'll phone Dr. Carter.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我给卡特医生打电话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 56.35,
      "end": 60.83,
      "text": "The doctor says that he will come at once.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "医生说他马上就来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 61.89,
      "end": 66.05,
      "text": "I'm sure that you need an x-ray, Andy.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "安迪，我敢肯定你需要拍X光片。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
